{"data":[{"date":"22:31 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh ch\u00ea '\u0111\u00e0n em' C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/tuan-manh-3-1522935681.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u00fd ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span> tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. Sau pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5m \u1ee9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \"L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i nghe th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi v\u0103ng t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi. C\u1eadu ta c\u00f2n d\u00f9ng m\u0169i gi\u00e0y ch\u1ecdc th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ec9nh.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1eadu ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec x\u00edch m\u00edch. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c ch\u00fa l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HAGL x\u1eed l\u00fd vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m h\u01a1n\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 80 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh b\u1ecb \u0111au sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf. V\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh c\u0169 \u1edf HAGL c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh c\u00e2u gi\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4068","checkdouble":"190719"},{"date":"23:02 08/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh' Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/hagl-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-chieu-mo-thu-mon-dt-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 'minh oan' cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u00ean ch\u1ea1y l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i: '\u0110\u1ee9ng d\u1eady \u0111i, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0 n\u1eb1m'. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a th\u1ea5y v\u1eady li\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea9y Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn x\u1ea5n l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n n\u00ean b\u1ecb th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u00ean k\u00ecm ch\u1ebf, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi l\u1ebd x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, khi\u00eau kh\u00edch khi\u1ebfn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1eefng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4067","checkdouble":"190720"},{"date":"00:11 09/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>1. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 32 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 hai CLB \u1edf nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 TP.HCM.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Diem-nhan-tran-HAGL-2-4-Khanh-Hoa-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a G\u1ed7\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u00e1ch V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd 'G\u1ed7' l\u00ean nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay anh \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 A S\u00e2n. Sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 39 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 44 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Youssouf Toure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, e r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong t\u1ed1p 5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, 'G\u1ed7' \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i khi hai t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb pha treo b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Josip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-2, song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HAGL gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh HAGL ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh gi\u1ecfi trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>3. M\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00f4m nay (8/7) g\u1eb7p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An khi anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng do l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 22, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c Ngh\u1ec7 An d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m nhanh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea9y ra. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 28, anh l\u1ea1i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai theo k\u00e8m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. Trong ph\u00fat n\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec h\u00f9ng h\u1ed5 g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, khi cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu l\u00e9p v\u1ebf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd phong t\u1ecfa g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u00edn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh r\u1ed3i m\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Toure c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng s\u1eafc l\u1ea1nh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t set qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 ngang ph\u00fat 84 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o thay anh l\u00e0 Ho\u00e0i An s\u00fat b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/36787800_1815071101918501_4864050149187387392_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i Pleiku gi\u00fap Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111ang c\u00f3 31 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 19, xem ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c nh\u1ecf, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HAGL c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean BXH. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sinh t\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4066","checkdouble":"190725"},{"date":"01:02 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">'Con t\u00e0u' H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018. Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, CLB TP.HCM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong kho\u1ea3ng 25 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-3 \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/DMH_3858(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i V-league. V\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TP.HCM l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a h\u00f2a nhau trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. 'G\u1ed7' v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm song sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V-League r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean V-League \u0111\u1ec3 '\u0103n ng\u1ee7' c\u00f9ng World Cup.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Oseni \u0111ang 't\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i' trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 th\u00ec c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Tien Linh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/nguyen-tien-linh-xuat-sac-nhat-vleague-thang-5.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Ti\u1ebfn Linh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Oseni xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 4 b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u00edt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a SLNA. S\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/Highlight-Quang-Nam-vs-Binh-Duong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>4. C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 TP.HCM v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t. N\u0103m nay V-League s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1,5 su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4065","checkdouble":"190726"},{"date":"01:14 09/07","title":"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TP.HCM, HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/thang-dam-clb-tphcm-hlv-ha-noi-van-khiem-ton-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TPHCM, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TPHCM, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Thang-dam-CLB-TPHCM,-HLV-Chu-Dinh-Nghiem-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch TP.HCM v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 6-3. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: \u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80%\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb khi l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB TP.HCM, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: \"Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 phung ph\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn l\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn CLB nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn CLB m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi-168-190726.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi-168-190726.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190695.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TPHCM (KT): Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson l\u1eadp poker trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4064","checkdouble":"190727"},{"date":"19:28 08/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/7: M.U \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/diem-tin-toi-87-mu-dai-chien-barca-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea, Barca ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba, Hazard l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 8/7.</h2><h2>M.U \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd The Sun, CLB M.U \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Barcelona trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Chelsea, Willian.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mourinho \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i The Blues s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i khi m\u00e0 Martial \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. Sau khi Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y Willian c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 87 MU \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 87 MU \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Diem-tin-toi-87-MU-dai-chien-Barca-vi-sao-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Ramon Calderon m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n si\u00eau sao Ronaldo.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cN\u1ebfu Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a trong v\u00f2ng 9 n\u0103m qua...\" c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd sao Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Star, CLB Everton \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Emil Forsberg.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Premier League c\u00f2n d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig. Ngo\u00e0i Everton th\u00ec Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>Wilshere s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp West Ham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Mirrror, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal Jack Wilshere s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn CLB West Ham theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb do v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, th\u1ee9 Hai 9/7. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 100 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng. Cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 30/6.</p>\r\n<h2>Hazard l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Marca (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Eden Hazard ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u00ean TTCN m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Hazard n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Neymar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp PSG v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n anh.</p>\r\n<h2>M.U theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Mexico</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Tuttomercatoweb, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hirving Lozano, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Mexico. Lozano \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB PSV c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Barca ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Don Balon (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Samul Umtiti c\u1ee7a Barca r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u euro).\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Barca, n\u01a1i anh s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 Umtiti, Dembele v\u00e0 Lucas Digne. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Pogba c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Lionel Messi.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXEM TH\u00caM:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-77-ronaldo-loi-keo-sao-real-toi-juventus-184-190626.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/7: Ronaldo l\u00f4i k\u00e9o sao Real t\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4063","checkdouble":"190701"},{"date":"06:17 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-97-choang-voi-doi-hoi-cua-neymar-voi-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/7.\r\n</h2><h2>Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris &ldquo;t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5&rdquo; Edinson Cavani, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luis Suarez &ndash; b\u1edfi Neymar r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 Brazil l\u1eabn Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 97 Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-97-Choang-voi-doi-hoi-cua-Neymar-voi-PSG-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7: Neymar l\u1ea1i ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Paulinho l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 sau 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y l\u1ea1i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, cho d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e3i 10 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y (chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paulinho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fernando Hierro ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ng\u00e0y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi La Roja \u1edf c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed G\u0110TT c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 chia tay trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Modric chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110ang m\u1ea3i chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Croatia v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf CLB. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh kh\u00f4ng b\u1eadn t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c CR7 s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Uruguay chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng quay l\u1ea1i Uruguay sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, m\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Torreira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Torreira tranh b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>R\u1ed9 tin Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 Mahrez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man xanh c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo Daily Mail, Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4062","checkdouble":"190728"},{"date":"20:30 08/07","title":"Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/14/neymar-muon-psg-rut-ruot-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mua Luis Suarez l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG b\u00e1n Cavani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Edison Cavani v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 28 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 30 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ligue 1. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn anh c\u00f3 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG mua Luis Suarez \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG mua Luis Suarez \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Neymar-muon-PSG-mua-Luis-Suarez-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG b\u00e1n Cavani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, anh c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao Neymar, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Cavani \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng\u00a0phai r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb PSG b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec7n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cavani-mau-thuan-voi-neymar-chelsea-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-172-168917.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Cavani</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG mua Suarez thay Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mua Luis Suarez l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Suarez ghi ban vao luoi Malaga\" title=\"Luis Suarez ghi ban vao luoi Malaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/luis-suarez-so-dung-do-liverpool-o-ban-ket-champions-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG mua Luis Suarez\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Suarez l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh\u00a0kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Suarez n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sport, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Suarez n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng Brazil d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n\u00a0n\u00e0y, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4061","checkdouble":"190707"},{"date":"21:01 08/07","title":"Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo t\u1edd Corriere dello Sport th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sang Real.</h2><h2>Real Madrid nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid tranh gianh Milinkovic-Savic voi M.U\" title=\"Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Sergej Milinkovic-Savic s\u1ebd chia tay Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y&quot; - \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfng \u00dd Corriere dello Sport ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 trong ng\u00e0y 7/7 v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Corriere dello Sport, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Savic l\u00e0 Mateja Kezman \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Savic s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Real Madrid. V\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 155 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Real, CLB Man United c\u0169ng \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Milinkovic-Savic hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n 4 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lazio. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4060","checkdouble":"190704"},{"date":"21:25 08/07","title":"M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/Man-Utd-transfer-news-979696.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang ch\u1ee7 Man United v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Man-Utd-transfer-news-979696.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 con trai Phil Neville</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trang ch\u1ee7 CLB Man United v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 10 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Harvey Neville - con trai c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Phil Neville. Harvey\u00a0chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M.U t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Valencia. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u1ea1i M.U gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1992, l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb M.U \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ea3n sinh ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harvey Neville, Mason Greenwood v\u00e0 c\u00e1c 'm\u1ea7m non' c\u1ee7a M.U c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U18 Premier League - danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua khi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U18 Man City.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Danh s\u00e1ch 10 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U h\u00e8 2018:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n:\u00a0Jacob Carney, Ondrej Mastny<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7:\u00a0Oliver Denham, Ben Hockenhull, Teden Mengi<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7:\u00a0Anthony Elanga, Max Haygarth, Mark Helm, Charlie McCann, Harvey Neville</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-duoc-dua-len-may-sau-phong-do-an-tuong-421-190711.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/jesse-lingard-duoc-dua-len-may-sau-phong-do-an-tuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-duoc-dua-len-may-sau-phong-do-an-tuong-421-190711.html\">Jesse Lingard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean m\u00e2y sau phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nCraig Milburn ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, HLV th\u1eddi ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-8-trung-ve-nam-trong-danh-sach-chuyen-nhuong-cua-mu-172-190703.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/day-danh-sach-8-trung-ve-nam-trong-danh-sach-chuyen-nhuong-cua-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-8-trung-ve-nam-trong-danh-sach-chuyen-nhuong-cua-mu-172-190703.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 8 trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a MU</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 danh s\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-87-mu-dai-chien-barca-vi-sao-chelsea-184-190701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/diem-tin-toi-87-mu-dai-chien-barca-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-87-mu-dai-chien-barca-vi-sao-chelsea-184-190701.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/7: M.U \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao Chelsea, Barca ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba, Hazard l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4059","checkdouble":"190708"},{"date":"21:08 08/07","title":"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea m\u00f9 t\u1ecbt v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/cac-cau-thu-chelsea-mu-tit-ve-nguoi-dan-dat-chelsea-o-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo Mirror, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a The Blues kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte hay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea m\u00f9 t\u1ecbt v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte, song \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Co-hay-khong-viec-Chelsea-sa-thai-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Chelsea sau m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a The Blues nh\u01b0\u00a0Cesc Fabregas , Marcos Alonso v\u00e0 Alvaro Morata \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf Cobham \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a The Blues kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte hay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng hay bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp kh\u1edfi tranh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Conte ra \u0111i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ESPN, Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c Conte ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, song \u00f4ng n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfp c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Blues s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/cac-cau-thu-chelsea-mu-tit-ve-nguoi-dan-dat-chelsea-o-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Antonio Conte nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Maurizio Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi HLV Sarri, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Napoli. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t. Chelsea c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Sun th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Willian, Courtois, Hazard v\u00e0 David Luiz s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu Conte ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Dailly Mail th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri</span> v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4058","checkdouble":"190710"},{"date":"22:25 08/07","title":"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua \"bom x\u1ecbt\" Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alvaro Morata \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Diego Costa. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMorata li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i Top 4, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Morata c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o tay Giroud, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u sao Real s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alvaro Morata \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/San-sang-nha-Higuain,-Juventus-muon-mua-Alvaro-Morata-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn ki\u00ean tr\u00ec theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Morata</span>, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1ea5t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i Higuain s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, Neymar mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n Edison Cavani. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Cavani ra \u0111i PSG s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Morata \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do trung phong ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNapoli v\u00e0 Dortmund c\u0169ng l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Morata. C\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4057","checkdouble":"190715"},{"date":"06:38 09/07","title":"Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/lindelof-tro-lai-mu-sau-that-bai-tai-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n Anh, \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga sau v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2>Lindelof tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0), Victor Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1t, anh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Lindelof v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, v\u00e0 Lindelof s\u1ebd s\u1edbm h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf CLB.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft vang l\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 Phil Jones, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn an \u1ee7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/lindelof.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lindelof chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd (c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U), b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u00f4m t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T Anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u1ea1i World Cup, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00fd h\u01a1n khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng&rdquo; &ndash; Lindelof chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, anh s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span><br>\r\nSau khi \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Zlatan Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi David Beckham.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4056","checkdouble":"190729"}]}